# Copy this file to ".Renviron" (which is git-ignored) and fill in your values.
# shinyapps.io credentials: https://www.shinyapps.io  ->  Account  ->  Tokens.
# These power dev/03_deploy.R for local/direct deploys. For CI deploys, set the
# same three values as GitHub repo secrets instead (Settings -> Secrets -> Actions).

SHINYAPPS_NAME=your-shinyapps-account-name
SHINYAPPS_TOKEN=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
SHINYAPPS_SECRET=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
